          "date": "2022-07-27 15:15:06.000000000",
          "tz": -360
        },
        "subject": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Repost imm buffers on correct EP",
        "message": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Repost imm buffers on correct EP\n\nPrior to this change, immediate buffers could be reposted on the EP\nassociated with the transaction instead of the EP associated with the\nimmediate buffer. This can cause EPs to have no immediate receive\nbuffers and prevent LNet from bring down the kfi interface.\n\nThis is fixed by always used the immediate buffer EP to repost when\nthe immediate buffer when references are returned.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-10210\nSigned-off-by: Ian Ziemba <ian.ziemba@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I327db55ebe23af641720d4d2c0a9320638d8f3d9\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
